# Cloudflare Pages redirects/rewrites. First match wins. Real files
# (/assets, /img, /sitemap.xml ...) and the root `/` index.html are served
# BEFORE these rules.
#
# NEVER add `/  /en  301` here: the SPA is served at the root `/`, so a
# root->/en redirect collides with root serving and produces an infinite
# redirect loop (ERR_TOO_MANY_REDIRECTS). Locale is handled client-side.

# Locale routes -> serve the SPA shell with 200 (URL preserved, app boots).
/en   /index.html   200
/vi   /index.html   200

# Everything else that is not a real file -> real 404 (kills soft-404).
/*    /404.html     404
